Company Overview of Emery Howard Portfolio Management, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Emery Howard Portfolio Management, Inc. is an employee owned investment manager. The firm provides its services to individuals, high net worth individuals, pension and profit sharing plans, and charitable organizations. It manages separate client focused equity and fixed income portfolios. The firm invests in the public equity and fixed income markets across the globe. It invests in exchange traded funds, institutional class mutual funds, and individual bonds while making its investments. Emery Howard Portfolio Management, Inc. was founded in 1991 and is based in San Mateo, California.


333 Lorton AvenueBurlingame, CA 94010United StatesFounded in 1991



Phone: 650-579-7100

Fax: 650-579-7313

www.emeryhoward.com







