How do I update this listing?




                                             Emery Howard Portfolio Management is based out of Burlingame. Emery Howard Portfolio Management is a large advisory firm with  More than 100 clients and discretionary assets under management (AUM) of $1,111,489,160 (Form ADV from 2017-01-31).  Their last reported 13F filing for Q1 2017 included $441,604,000 in managed 13F securities
    and a top 10 holdings concentration of 83.09%. Emery Howard Portfolio Management's largest holding is SPDR S&P 500 ETF Index Depositary Receipts with shares held of 578,264.  Emery Howard Portfolio Management has met the qualifications for inclusion in our WhaleScore system.    WhaleWisdom has at least 46 13F filings in our database for Emery Howard Portfolio Management. 
                                           






